-- Simmers Says Bernard Swanepoel Will Take Over as Chairman From September
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-07-27T13:22:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/simmers-says-bernard-swanepoel-will-take-over-as-chairman-from-september.html

          
          
             Simmer & Jack Mines Ltd. said its
board has elected Bernard Swanepoel to take over as chairman
after its annual general meeting on Sept. 10.  
          
          


  


        